# --- Sensitive documents: never commit ---
# Source documents containing PII/financial data live in a controlled store
# outside git, not in this repo. This folder and any sensitive-docs folder
# are ignored so they can never be committed accidentally.
docs/weldon-pre-purchase-docs/
**/sensitive/
**/*private-docs*/

# Common sensitive source-document types (defense in depth)
*.pdf
*.xlsx
*.docx

# Windows / WSL metadata clutter
*:Zone.Identifier
